{
  "stem": "24163.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I walked in the door, my-- my boss, who was a Gentile, married to a Jewish woman, my boss said, Herman, I don't think you ought to stay here today.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, why not?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, well, during the night, there were some pogroms against Jews in the city of Cologne.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To the best of my knowledge, they set fire to part of the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And since everyone in-- in Germany always had to register, the German police knew where anyone was at any given time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they certainly knew where I lived and where I worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, I don't think it's a good idea that you are going to be here today, because if they come to arrest you-- and I heard there have already been some arrests-- if they come to arrest you, you're just simply not here.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, you better leave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I walked out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I walked the streets of Cologne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first thing I did, I went over to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, I got within one block of the synagogue, and I saw the talismans and the prayer books laying on the street-- I think some of them were-- were even burning-- and people are milling around the synagogues who were not Jewish people, believe me.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was concerned to get closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And obviously, what my boss had told me was correct.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I turned around, and I walked away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I walked down the streets of Cologne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there's a very famous street called the [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Ringe Strasse, ?] which is around-- it goes-- circles around Cologne.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as I walked along, there were truckloads of stormtroopers coming up and down the ring, with German flags in the truck, yelling anti-Semitic slogans.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
